                    cord
                    blood samples. Generally 1 in 10 samples are of storing quality; so by the end we will have a
                    repository
                    of 10,000 units," said Abhaya.
                    <br>
                    <br>
                    He said consent of the parent will be taken before releasing the unit to a needy patient.

